high_descs: Turn to the right and move to the sink area.
Pick up the knife that in on the counter.
Slice the tomato that is on the counter to your right.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Move toward the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the tomato inside.  Allow to cool. Open fridge. Pick up tomato. Close fridge
Turn left and move across room to the microwave.
Open microwave.  Put the tomato in the microwave. Close the door.
Turn right, then go across the room to the stove and then turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink.
Pick up the tomato to the left of the sink.
Cut the tomato in half and place it to the left of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and pick up the cut tomato to the left of the sink.
Turn right and move towards the refrigerator then turn left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge,  put tomato in top shelf of fridge, close fridge, open fridge and get tomato slice, then close the fridge.
Turn left to face microwave and then move to microwave.
Open the microwave, put the cut tomato on the plate in the microwave, then close the microwave
anns.task_desc: Warm up a tomato slice in the microwave.

high_descs: turn right and head over to the stove straight ahead, then turn right and go to the sink straight ahead
grab the knife off of the counter on the left
cut up the tomato on your left
place the knife inside of the sink
grab a tomato slice from the left off of the kitchen sink
turn right and walk to the fridge at the end of the kitchen counters on your left
place the tomato slice inside of the fridge, then take it back out
turn left and walk straight forwards to the microwave at the end of the room
place the tomato slice inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled tomato slice inside of the microwave
